看着我！
Look at me!

579
00:36:11,403 --> 00:36:13,343
你一边是黑色，另一边是白色
You're black on one side and white on the other.

580
00:36:13,973 --> 00:36:16,214
我右边是黑色的
I am black on the right side.

581
00:36:20,779 --> 00:36:23,635
 我没有看到显着差异
I fail to see the significant difference.

582
00:36:23,941 --> 00:36:25,458
洛凯右边是白色的
Lokai is white on the right side.

583
00:36:25,458 --> 00:36:27,557
他们种族右边都是白色的
All of his people are white on the right side.

584
00:36:33,327 --> 00:36:36,637
专员，或许我的母星瓦肯的经历
Commissioner, perhaps the experience of my own planet Vulcan

585
