At the moment, I seem to have no choice.

668
00:41:35,882 --> 00:41:38,531
所以这就是阿里安纳斯之后的正义
So this is justice after Ariannus!

669
00:41:38,974 --> 00:41:41,269
你签了我的死刑执行令，我警告过你会发生什么
You have signed my death warrant. I warned you what to expect.

670
00:41:42,884 --> 00:41:46,636
你会继续让这种对正义的嘲弄继续下去吗？
Will you continue to let this mockery of justice go on?

671
00:41:47,011 --> 00:41:50,467
如果你是正义的拥护者，请证明这一点！杀了他！
If you are partisans of justice, prove it! Kill him!

672
00:41:50,665 --> 00:41:52,714
[契科夫]我们不是杀手
[Chekov] We are not killers.

673
00:41:53,049 --> 00:41:55,225
你能做什么？只在嘴上伸张正义吗？
What do you do? Carry justice on your tongues?

674
00:41:55,609 --> 00:41:57,619
你只会为它乞求，但你不会为它而战或死
You will beg for it, but you won't fight or die for it.

675
00:41:57,875 --> 00:42:00,958
经过多年的领导战斗，你似乎很有活力
After so many years of leading the fight, you seem very much alive.

676
00:42:01,164 --> 00:42:04,365
我怀疑他的许多追随者也能这样说
I doubt that the same can be said for many of his followers.

677
00:42:04,552 --> 00:42:06,222
你完了，洛凯！
You're finished, Lokai!

678
00:42:06,297 --> 00:42:10,688
我们已经把你的种族关在了谢隆上
We've got your kind penned in on Cheron into little districts.

679
00:42:10,688 --> 00:42:11,725
那不会改变
It's not going to change.

680
00:42:11,803 --> 00:42:15,000
你搜寻了整个银河系，一无所获，除了单色垃圾
You've combed the galaxy and come up with nothing but mono-coloured trash,

681
00:42:15,073 --> 00:42:17,007
行善者和流血的心
do-gooders and bleeding hearts.

682
00:42:17,075 --> 00:42:19,543
你死定了，你这个半白人
You're dead, you half-white!

683
00:42:21,010 --> 00:42:22,695
你这个没用的无聊家伙
You useless pieces of bland flesh.

684
00:42:24,448 --> 00:42:26,875
我要带你走，你个半黑！
I'll take you with me, you half-black.

685
00:42:29,865 --> 00:42:32,130
贝尔，你再这样下去
Bele, you keep this up,

686
00:42:32,130 --> 00:42:33,982
就永远无法和你的囚犯一起去谢隆了
and you'll never get to Cheron with your prisoner.

687
00:42:34,436 --> 00:42:36,522
飞船的舰桥将受到不可挽回的损坏
The rest of this ship will be irreparably damaged.

688
00:42:36,862 --> 00:42:39,126
这将是你们最后的战场
This will be your final battlefield.

689
00:42:39,197 --> 00:42:43,634
你5万年的追寻都白费了
Your 50,000 years of pursuit will have been wasted.

690
00:42:47,205 --> 00:42:52,084
而你，洛凯，将在太空中死去
And you, Lokai, you'll die here in space.

691
00:42:53,011 --> 00:42:57,243
你不会激励更多的信徒，你的事业将结束
You'll inspire no more disciples. Your cause will be ended.

692
00:42:57,316 --> 00:43:01,753
记住，舰长，政治庇护所是我的权利
Remember, Captain, political sanctuary is my right.

693
00:43:02,485 --> 00:43:05,715
我是你的俘虏，尊重这一权利
I am your prisoner. Honour that right,

694
00:43:06,058 --> 00:43:08,822
否则战斗会继续，你的船会被烧毁
or the fight will go on and your ship will burn up.

695
00:43:09,606 --> 00:43:10,623
你说到点子上了
You've made your point.

696
00:43:10,696 --> 00:43:12,492
如果你听他的诡计
If you listen to his legalistic trickery,

697
00:43:12,492 --> 00:43:15,096
我将不得不摧毁这艘船
I shall have to destroy this ship and everybody aboard.

698
00:43:15,693 --> 00:43:16,913
我明白了
I understand.

699
00:43:17,879 --> 00:43:21,437
你会把企业号归还给我吗？
Will you return the Enterprise to my control?

700
00:43:30,555 --> 00:43:31,756
为什么不？
Why not?

701
00:43:44,038 --> 00:43:46,995
斯科提，方向控制维修是否已经完成？
Scotty, have repairs on directional control been completed?

702
00:43:47,065 --> 00:43:49,090
是的，长官，已改道
Aye, sir, rerouted.

703
00:43:49,167 --> 00:43:52,038
检查控制器和坐标
Check controls and coordinates.

704
00:43:52,437 --> 00:43:55,503
[苏鲁]控制器操作中，企业号一如既往地作出响应
[Sulu] Controls operating. The Enterprise is responding.

705
00:43:55,857 --> 00:43:57,039
舰长，真不错  
Captain, it's beautiful. 

706
00:43:57,039 --> 00:43:58,526
锁定坐标
Locking onto coordinates.

707
00:43:58,635 --> 00:44:01,560
舰长，我们在谢隆的扫描范围内
Captain, we are within scanning range of Cheron.

708
00:44:05,183 --> 00:44:06,780
是否在可视范围内？  
Is it within visual range? 

709
00:44:06,780 --> 00:44:08,983
现在进入范围内，舰长
Coming within visual range now, Captain.

710
00:44:09,272 --> 00:44:11,318
契科夫，把它放在屏幕上，最大放大倍数
Chekov, put it on the screen, extreme magnification.

711
00:44:17,929 --> 00:44:19,338
你扫描到了什么？  
What are you picking up? 

712
00:44:19,338 --> 00:44:23,458
几个非常大的城市，无人居住
Several large cities, uninhabited.

713
00:44:24,321 --> 00:44:27,857
巨大的交通系统，没有交通
Extensive traffic systems, barren of traffic.

714
00:44:28,907 --> 00:44:33,571
低等动物和植物侵占城市
Lower animal sand vegetation encroaching on the cities.

715
00:44:33,645 --> 00:44:37,445
根本没有智能生命形式显示，舰长
No sapient life-forms registering at all, Captain.

716
00:44:37,814 --> 00:44:40,314
[史波克]没有自然灾害的证据
[Spock] There is no evidence of natural disaster,

717
00:44:40,385 --> 00:44:43,912
然而，还有大量未掩埋的尸体
yet there are vast numbers of unburied corpses in all cities.

718
00:44:44,187 --> 00:44:48,855
你的意思是…所有的人都死了？
You mean, all the people are dead?

719
00:44:50,658 --> 00:44:52,094
都死了，舰长
All dead, Captain.

720
00:44:52,332 --> 00:44:55,607
他们已经彻底消灭了对方
They have annihilated each other totally.

721
00:44:56,912 --> 00:45:00,723
我的人民，都死了？
My people, my... all dead?

722
00:45:01,139 --> 00:45:03,905
是的，专员，所有人
Yes, Commissioner, all of them.

723
00:45:04,949 --> 00:45:06,288
没有一个活着？  
No one alive? 

724
00:45:06,643 --> 00:45:08,402
完全没有，先生
None at all, sir.

725
00:45:09,981 --> 00:45:14,044
是你们这帮凶手干的！
Your band of murderers did this.

726
00:45:14,386 --> 00:45:17,355
是你们的种族灭绝狂做的！
Your insane asylum maniacs did this!

727
00:45:17,422 --> 00:45:19,720
停下来！你们两个怎么了？
Stop it! What's the matter with you two?

728
00:45:19,791 --> 00:45:22,726
你们没听到史波克说的吗？你的星球已经死了
Didn't you hear Spock? Your planet is dead!

729
00:45:23,140 --> 00:45:25,898
因为仇恨谢隆上已经没有活人了
There's nobody alive on Cheron because of hate.

730
00:45:26,598 --> 00:45:29,012
你为之奋斗的目标已不复存在
The cause you fought about no longer exists.

731
00:45:29,901 --> 00:45:32,426
花点时间喘口气，放弃你们的仇恨
Give yourselves time to breathe. Give up your hate.

732
00:45:33,826 --> 00:45:36,702
欢迎你们和我们一起生活
You're welcome to live with us.

733
00:45:37,077 --> 00:45:39,266
听我说
Listen to me.

734
00:45:39,344 --> 00:45:42,513
如果你们不停止仇恨
You both must end up dead

735
00:45:43,173 --> 00:45:45,044
你们俩最后都会死
if you don't stop hating.

736
00:45:45,468 --> 00:45:47,586
你是一个理想主义的梦想家
You're an idealistic dreamer.

737
00:45:52,511 --> 00:45:53,515
贝尔
Bele?

738
00:45:56,449 --> 00:45:58,440
 追捕结束了
The chase is finished.

739
00:45:58,517 --> 00:46:01,111
他逃不出我的手心
He must not escape me.

740
00:46:01,394 --> 00:46:03,280
他能去哪里？
Where can he go?

741
00:46:10,674 --> 00:46:11,332
贝尔？
Bele?

742
00:46:12,169 --> 00:46:14,001
先生，我要通知警卫吗？  
Shall I alert security, sir? 

743
00:46:14,641 --> 00:46:16,207
不，上尉
No, Lieutenant.

744
00:46:17,478 --> 00:46:18,817
他们能跑到哪里去？
Where can they run?

745
00:46:38,062 --> 00:46:41,381
[史波克]舰长，我用船上的传感器上找到了他们
[Spock] Captain, I have located them on ship's sensors.

746
00:46:41,381 --> 00:46:41,623
贝尔在3号甲板上追逐洛凯
Bele is chasing Lokai on deck 3.

747
00:46:41,623 --> 00:46:46,404
贝尔在3号甲板上追逐洛凯
Bele is chasing Lokai on deck 3.

748
00:47:04,895 --> 00:47:07,836
贝尔正在经过3号娱乐室
Bele is passing recreation room 3,

749
00:47:08,043 --> 00:47:09,766
接近船员休息室
approaching the crewmen's lounge.

750
00:47:10,397 --> 00:47:13,391
洛凯跑过船员休息室
Lokai is running past the crewmen's lounge.

751
00:47:28,485 --> 00:47:31,010
洛凯刚刚抵达5号甲板
Lokai has just arrived on deck 5.

752
00:47:51,704 --> 00:47:54,028
经过3号娱乐室.
Passing recreation room 3.

753
00:47:59,616 --> 00:48:01,100
[传送装置嗡嗡声]
[Transporter Whirring]

754
00:48:02,152 --> 00:48:04,803
[传送装置嗡嗡声]
[Transporter Humming]

755
00:48:05,660 --> 00:48:08,270
舰长，有人激活了传送装置
Captain, someone has activated the transporter mechanism.

756
00:48:08,684 --> 00:48:10,230
史波克，传送室里有人吗？
Spock, anyone in the transporter room?

757
00:48:10,379 --> 00:48:12,732
没有，舰长，传送室是空的
Negative, Captain. Transporter room is clear.

758
00:48:12,978 --> 00:48:18,228
然而，有一个生命形式正在星球上物质化
However, there is a life-form materializing on the planet.

759
00:48:19,636 --> 00:48:23,970
是洛凯，他回到了谢隆
It is Lokai. He is back on Cheron.

760
00:48:24,364 --> 00:48:27,594
那里没人会审判他，他的法官都死了
There's nobody there to try him. His judges are all dead.

761
00:48:41,629 --> 00:48:44,327
舰长，传送装置再次被激活
Captain, the transporter mechanism has been activated again.

762
00:48:45,874 --> 00:48:46,977
当然  
Of course. 

763
00:48:47,194 --> 00:48:48,514
是贝尔，舰长
It is Bele, Captain.

764
00:48:48,760 --> 00:48:51,888
[传送装置嗡嗡声]
[Transporter Whirring]

765
00:48:52,235 --> 00:48:55,290
[传送装置嗡嗡声]
[Transporter Humming]

766
00:48:58,018 --> 00:49:02,574
而另一个生命形式出现在谢隆上
And another life-form has appeared on Cheron.

767
00:49:09,315 --> 00:49:10,694
这没有任何意义
It doesn't make any sense.

768
00:49:13,442 --> 00:49:18,317
期望从这种极端观点的两种心态中获得理智
To expect sense from two mentalities of such extreme viewpoints

769
00:49:18,809 --> 00:49:20,795
是不合逻辑的
is not logical.

770
00:49:20,864 --> 00:49:23,586
但是他们的星球已经死了，谁是对的重要吗？
But their planet's dead. Does it matter now which one's right?

771
00:49:23,823 --> 00:49:29,062
对洛凯和贝尔来说不是这样，对他们来说重要的是他们的仇恨
Not to Lokai and Bele. All that matters to them is their hate.

772
00:49:29,246 --> 00:49:31,357
你认为这就是他们所拥有的一切吗？
Do you suppose that's all they ever had, sir?

773
00:49:31,875 --> 00:49:36,361
不，但他们只剩下这些了
No. But that's all they have left.

774
00:49:37,572 --> 00:49:43,235
曲速2，苏鲁先生，设定去星际基地4的航线
Warp factor 2, Mr. Sulu. Set course for Star base 4.

